">❌</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbpaifc-r6tqbh-877\"><a id=\"_o3tbg847x4p1\" display=\"false\"></a>Industry Restriction</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifc-jdqi7u-878\"><strong>Industry</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifc-2siifv-879\"><strong>List of Business</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"4\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifc-qkwunu-880\">Pornographic/adult services/night club</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifc-knqv9x-881\">Sale of dangerous products/services, i.e. weaponry, illegal drugs, and narcotics</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifd-vpgkv4-882\">Gambling</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifd-bf005z-883\">Sale of fake/imitated goods in which breaches the intellectual/property rights</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifd-swy49c-884\">Merchants that indicated/suspected as platform offering illegal cash-out (gesek tunai/gestun)</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifd-lbh322-885\">Financial businesses</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifd-pct29r-886\"> Donation</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"7\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifd-3sa70l-887\">Non-financial businesses that require licensing</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaife-e507r6-888\"> Sale of alcohol/liquor/booze without license</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaife-gi8wpx-889\"> Cigarette / Liquid smoke</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaife-eu5epj-890\"> Selling followers, like, etc</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaife-q4ktxq-891\"> Top up game cash</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaife-dtk7z5-892\"> Top up pulsa, e-wallet etc</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaife-xjewv6-893\"> Payment Point</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaiff-73tjs6-894\"> Business which product/services is yet to be licensed by authorities</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbpaiff-r0972j-895\"><a id=\"_ujkex4eg0uw0\" display=\"false\"></a>SLA</h2><ul data-block-id=\"mmbpaiff-ryyzdh-896\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbpaiff-9bsc9w-897\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkadwdj-ynf2i3-263\">SLA for most merchants registering <strong>from Sept 9th onwards</strong> - instantly activated upon Go-Live as long as they pass the eligibility and industry restrictions</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbpaiff-yl2pva-898\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkadwdj-c8nwsn-264\">For existing/old merchants requesting manually thru #mo-request: 1-2 working days</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbpaiff-kb1u7w-899\"><a id=\"_r0miqi6pvfyc\" display=\"false\"></a>Onboarding Flow</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaiff-5nf8nw-900\"><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaiff-nja2jz-901\"><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaiff-ki0ygt-902\"><strong>Action</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifg-kpkos6-903\"><strong>Process Owner</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifg-zmhmnc-904\">Merchant register Xendit</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifg-fy7sy1-905\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifg-f2pip9-906\">After the merchant passes KYC, we only need thick Indomaret then click save and merchant’s Indomaret CA will active<img data-block-id=\"mmbpaifg-4bhrpv-907\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-indomaret-image-k8i047kp.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifg-lgvdef-908\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifh-qsv9q1-909\">Activation using retool</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifh-ecg0jv-910\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifh-0blmc7-911\">In case activation via IA fail, or maybe agent forgot to thick Indomaret option when set merchant to live, we can still active manually via retool</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifh-ic4k5d-912\">With this link</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifh-2a7d8x-913\"><a href=\"https://retool.tidnex.com/apps/60f2bb00-bc03-11ee-8011-ff0540a826eb/Payments%20Beta%20CS/%5BRO%20ID%5D%5BPROD-LIVE%5D%20Activate%20Indomaret%20Aggregator\"><u>https://retool.tidnex.com/apps/60f2bb00-bc03-11ee-8011-ff0540a826eb/Payments%20Beta%20CS/%5BRO%20ID%5D%5BPROD-LIVE%5D%20Activate%20Indomaret%20Aggregator</u></a></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifh-fbn5s0-914\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpaifh-yct9m4-915\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-indomaret-image-e5hd7wmd.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifh-nu3hhf-916\">We only need input BID then click submit and their Indomaret will activate..</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpaifh-vrgiet-917\">MO</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbpaifh-cmb4q8-918\"><a id=\"_vo1m3khr1obl\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><p data-block-id=\"mmkadwdl-mbbb9y-265\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Indomaret","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Indomaret","Slug":"indomaret-1","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"Indomaret","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"Indomaret","Slug":"indomaret-1","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"Indomaret","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Indomaret","Slug":"indomaret-1","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"Indomaret","Description":null}]